<h1><i class="fa fa-trash-alt"></i>Deleting Your Account</h1>

<ol class="breadcrumb">
	<li><a href="#help"><i class="fa fa-question-circle"></i>Help</a></li>
	<li><a href="#help/managing-account"><i class="fa fa-user"></i>Managing Your Account</a></li>
	<li><i class="fa fa-trash-alt"></i>Deleting Your Account</li>
</ol>

<div class="content">
	<p>If you would like to delete your account, you may do so, which will permanantly delete all files, images, and data that you have entered.</p>

	<ol>
		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-cog"></i>Launch the Settings App</h2>
			<p>Click on the settings icon in the session toolbar at the top of the screen in order to launch the <a href="#apps/settings-browser">Settings</a> app.</p>

			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/apps/managing-account/deleting-account/launch-settings-manager.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Settings Icon"><img src="images/help/managing-account/deleting-account/settings-icon.png" height="40px" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Settings Icon</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-user"></i>Click on the Account Icon</h2>
			<p>In the <a href="#apps/settings-browser">Settings</a> app, note the array of icons for various system settings. Click on the icon labelled "Account".</p>

			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/info/apps/settings-browser/settings-browser.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Settings"><img class="dialog" src="images/info/apps/settings-browser/settings-browser.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Settings</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-trash-alt"></i>Click on Delete Account Button</h2>
			<p>At the top of the Account Settings dialog, you will see your current account info. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/help/managing-account/deleting-account/account-settings.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Account Settings"><img class="dialog" src="images/help/managing-account/deleting-account/account-settings.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Account Settings</div>
			</div>

			<p>If you scroll to the bottom of this page, you will see a button labelled "Delete Account". Click this button to delete your account and all of its associated data. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/help/managing-account/deleting-account/delete-account.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Delete Account Button"><img class="dialog" src="images/help/managing-account/deleting-account/delete-account.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Delete Account Button</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-question-circle"></i>Confirm Delete</h2>
			<p>You will be presented with a dialog box to confirm your account deletion.  Press "Ok" to continue.  When you delete your account, all of your data will be deleted and you will be logged out. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/help/managing-account/deleting-account/confirm-delete-account-dialog.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Confirm Delete Account Dialog"><img class="dialog" src="images/help/managing-account/deleting-account/confirm-delete-account-dialog.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Confirm Delete Account Dialog</div>
			</div>
		</li>
	</ol>
</div>